Title: 数据流/状态流图
Describe: state、channel、checkpoint、thread_id 和 tool messages 的数据生命周期。
------------------------------------------------------------
[Example]
S07_DATA_OR_STATE_FLOW：图运行状态生命周期

[Description]
LangGraph 的状态不是单个 mutable dict 在节点间传递，而是通过 channel update、reducer、版本号、checkpoint 和 pending writes 共同推进。

[UML]
@startuml
state "No Thread State" as New
state "Input Checkpoint" as Input
state "Loop Checkpoint" as Loop
state "Interrupted" as Interrupted
state "Resumed" as Resumed
state "Completed" as Completed
state "Errored" as Errored

[*] --> New
New --> Input : invoke/stream with input
Input --> Loop : prepare_next_tasks
Loop --> Loop : apply_writes and create checkpoint
Loop --> Interrupted : interrupt_before/after or GraphInterrupt
Interrupted --> Resumed : Command(resume) / config resume
Resumed --> Loop : resume remaining supersteps
Loop --> Completed : no more tasks / finish point
Loop --> Errored : unhandled node/checkpoint error
Completed --> [*]
Errored --> [*]
@enduml

[Detail]
状态转移来自 `CheckpointMetadata.source` 的 `input/loop/update/fork` 语义、`Checkpoint` 中 `channel_values/channel_versions/versions_seen/updated_channels` 字段，以及 `PregelLoop` 管理 step、stop、is_replaying、checkpointer、store、stream 等运行状态。`thread_id` 是 checkpoint 的主要索引，缺失时 checkpointer 无法提供跨调用恢复。

图中 `Interrupted -> Resumed` 是维护时最容易破坏的路径：interrupt 不只是异常，它还要求 checkpoint 和 pending writes 保持足够信息，后续 resume 才能从正确 task 和 namespace 继续。
------------------------------------------------------------
[Example]
Tool calling 数据流

[Description]
在 prebuilt agent 中，LLM 输出 `AIMessage.tool_calls`，`ToolNode` 转成工具调用请求并返回 `ToolMessage` 或 `Command`，再由 graph state 中的 `messages` reducer 聚合。

[UML]
@startuml
left to right direction
component "AIMessage.tool_calls" as Calls
component "ToolCallRequest" as Request
component "BaseTool / Callable" as Tool
component "ToolMessage" as ToolMessage
component "Command" as Command
component "messages state" as Messages
component "InjectedState / InjectedStore / ToolRuntime" as Injection

Calls --> Request : parse and validate
Injection --> Request : inject state, store, runtime
Request --> Tool : execute
Tool --> ToolMessage : normal result
Tool --> Command : state/control update
ToolMessage --> Messages : append via reducer
Command --> Messages : update state or route
@enduml

[Detail]
`ToolNode` 的模块注释明确其设计模式：并行执行多个 tool call、可配置错误处理、state 注入、store 注入和 Command-based state updates。`ToolCallRequest` 在 `libs/prebuilt/langgraph/prebuilt/tool_node.py:133`，`ToolNode` 在 `:622`，`ToolRuntime` 在 `:1663`，`InjectedState` 和 `InjectedStore` 分别在 `:1753`、`:1829`。
